            <taskString>Let the minced meat mixture cool in the fridge for an hour. 
</taskString>
            <timerString>Minced meat mixture resting</timerString>
            <alertString>Task out the minced meat mixture from the fridge.</alertString>
            <taskTitle>Rest the meatball mix</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>3</ID>
            <parents>2</parents>
            <children>4</children>
            <time>600</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Boil water in a selected saucepan adding a bit of butter. Form the meatballs into round balls with a tablespoon - and dip the spoon regularly in the boiling water to shape the round meat balls in the palm of your hand. </taskString>
            <timerString></timerString>
            <alertString></alertString>
            <taskTitle>Forming the meatballs</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>4</ID>
            <parents>3</parents>
            <children>7</children>
            <time>660</time>
            <attentionRequired>false</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Cook the raw meatballs in boiling water for about 11 minutes.</taskString>
            <timerString>Cooking the meatballs</timerString>
            <alertString>Drain the meatballs for water.</alertString>
            <taskTitle>Cooking the meatballs</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>5</ID>
            <parents>0</parents>
            <children>6</children>
            <time>900</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Melt the butter in a pan and add flour - then whip it constantly together into a smooth dough. After that - finely dice the onion and mix the mild curry powder and onion together in the sauce. Boil the sauce together for some minutes while stirring. Add the cream.</taskString>
            <timerString></timerString>
            <alertString></alertString>
            <taskTitle>Mild curry sauce</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>6</ID>
            <parents>5</parents>
            <children>7</children>
            <time>90</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Season to taste with salt - pepper - and the dish must not be spicy hot. That is the secret of the dish - as it must leave the meal with a smooth and mild curry flavour.</taskString>
            <timerString></timerString>
            <alertString></alertString>
            <taskTitle>Season the curry sauce</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>7</ID>
            <parents>6,4</parents>
            <children>9</children>
            <time>3600</time>
            <attentionRequired>false</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Put the meatballs in the mild curry sauce and lat them rest - while they soak up the curry sauce for at least 1 hour to flavour the entire dish.</taskString>
            <timerString>Meatballs and curry sauce resting</timerString>
            <alertString>The meatballs and the curry sauce have finished resting.</alertString>
            <taskTitle>Meatballs and mild curry sauce</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>8</ID>
            <parents>0</parents>
            <children>9</children>
            <time>600</time>
            <attentionRequired>false</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Fill the saucepan with a tight-fitting lid with 2dl long-grain white rice - after rinsing the rice in cold water. Then top up with 3 times as much water over the amount of rice. Let the water boil over the rice for 10 minutes.</taskString>
            <timerString>Boiling rice</timerString>
            <alertString>The rice has finished boiling. Turn off the heat and let the lid stay on the saucepan while the rice soaks up the remaining water.</alertString>
            <taskTitle>Fluffy White Rice</taskTitle>
        </task>
		
		<task>
            <ID>9</ID>
            <parents>7,8</parents>
            <children>0</children>
            <time>240</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
